==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Hand over the money with one hand, get the goods with the other hand.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī shŏu jīao qían, yī shŏu jīao hùo

===Phrase===
'''一手交钱,一手交货''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# {{idiom}} Do things in a simple and direct manner.

===Alternate forms===
一手交錢,一手交貨 ([[Traditional Chinese]])

